<a href="http://teamon.jogger.pl/2009/08/19/prosty-960-gridder">published at Jogger</a>.</div><div class="lead"><p>Mimo iż <a href="http://960.gs">System 960.gs</a> zapewnia bookmarklet włączający siatkę na dowolnej stronie postanowiłem naskrobać swój - prostszy i (imho) ładniejszy ;]</p>

<p>Smacznego:
 <a href="javascript:(function(){document.body.appendChild(document.createElement(&amp;#x27;script&amp;#x27;)).src=&amp;#x27;http://s.teamon.eu/960gs/960gridder.js&amp;#x27;;})();">Przeciągnij mnie!</a></p>

<p>Kod: </p></p>
<pre class="highlight javascript"><span class="c1">// use with bookmarklet
// javascript:(function(){document.body.appendChild(document.createElement('script')).src='http://s.teamon.eu/960gs/960gridder.js';})();
</span>

<span class="nx">g</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="nb">document</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="nx">getElementById</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="s2">"gridoverlay"</span><span class="p">)</span>
<span class="k">if</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="nx">g</span><span class="p">){</span>
  <span class="k">if</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="nx">g</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="nx">style</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="nx">display</span> <span class="o">==</span> <span class="s2">"none"</span><span class="p">)</span> <span class="nx">g</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="nx">style</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="nx">display</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="s2">"block"</span>
  <span class="k">else</span> <span class="nx">g</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="nx">style</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="nx">display</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="s2">"none"</span>
<span class="p">}</span> <span class="k">else</span> <span class="p">{</span>
  <span class="nx">g</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="nb">document</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="nx">createElement</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="s1">'div'</span><span class="p">)</span>
  <span class="nx">g</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="nx">id</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="s2">"gridoverlay"</span>
  <span class="nx">g</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="nx">style</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="nx">width</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="s2">"960px"</span>
  <span class="nx">g</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="nx">style</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="nx">height</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="nb">document</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="nx">height</span> <span class="o">+</span> <span class="s2">"px"</span>
  <span class="nx">g</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="nx">style</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="nx">backgroundImage</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="s2">"url(http://s.teamon.eu/960gs/12_col.png)"</span>
  <span class="nx">g</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="nx">style</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="nx">position</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="s2">"absolute"</span>
  <span class="nx">g</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="nx">style</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="nx">left</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="s2">"50%"</span>
  <span class="nx">g</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="nx">style</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="nx">top</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="s2">"0"</span>
  <span class="nx">g</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="nx">style</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="nx">marginLeft</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="s2">"-480px"</span>
  <span class="nb">document</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="nx">body</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="nx">appendChild</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="nx">g</span><span class="p">)</span>
<span class="p">}</span>
